cdata.name: ZCC Coin
cdata.desc: ZCCCoin (ZCC) is forked from YaCoin a hybrid scrypt PoW + PoS based crypto currency and scrypt-jane algorithm with improved parameters. The total number of coins is set to one billion and there are 520 confirmations needed for mining rewards to be distributed. The block reward is again linked to the the dificulty which is in turn related to the network power. So the more network power, the higher the difficulty, and the lower the block reward.
